{"tid":2012989,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺疫苗有望9月推出但疫苗玻璃樽短缺 專家：單供應美國也要兩年生產","createTime":"2020-05-12T04:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T05:55:19.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a671c569a831f90aa1fb87663b51b135292842","tid":2012989,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/05/11/phpukE4Kk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F11%2FphpukE4Kk.jpg&h=b3583523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情已造成全球超過28萬人死亡，各大藥廠則正緊急研發疫苗，但有多位專家指出，即使最快在9月便有獲批准使用的疫苗，製造商出於供應鏈延誤，恐沒有足夠的疫苗專用包裝玻璃瓶，因此無法即時大量供應全球約80億人口的疫苗，甚至足夠美國使用的疫苗玻璃瓶，就可能約需兩年的生產時間。<br />\n<br />\n《Business Insider》8日報導，雖然外界普遍預期，武漢肺炎疫苗有望在今年9月獲得批准使用，但最近被免職美國生物醫學高階研究和發展管理局（BARDA）局長職位的Rick Bright博士警告，要生產足夠的疫苗專用玻璃瓶以滿足美國的疫苗需求，恐需要兩年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n牛津大學醫學欽定教授（Regius Professor of Medicine at the University of Oxford）John Bell爵士也在4月30日稱，能生產疫苗的藥廠都在搶購疫苗藥瓶，造成現在全世界的專用瓶只剩2億個。<br />\n<br />\n世界第5大製藥企業賽諾菲（Sanofi）前研究副總裁Jeffrey Almond教授稱，如果現在藥瓶廠沒有沒日沒夜地加班，他會感到很驚訝，因為現在很顯然需要增加藥瓶的產量。<br />\n<br />\n而據流行病防備創新聯盟（CEPI）副總裁James Robinson，衛生醫用品大廠嬌生（J&amp;J）已經訂購了2.5億個疫苗藥瓶，且市面上的藥評恐已被嬌生買光。<br />\n<br />\n發明一次性針筒的柯斯卡（Marc Koska）也表示，世界各地包括中國在內，恐需要許多個月甚至幾年，才能生產約10億個供歐洲人注射兩次的藥瓶。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，疫苗藥瓶是由專用玻璃製成，通常容納2毫升至100毫升的液體、平均高度為45公釐、寬為11.5公釐，其除了要承受寒冷的溫度外，還要能承受在全球範圍內運輸下可能的磨損。此外，裝瓶疫苗的過程也很艱鉅，每個藥瓶在透過機器瓶裝完疫苗後，都要經過手工檢查，因此要生產供全球約80億人使用的疫苗，絕非易事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3161973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3161973&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HUV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=745ae7ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3161973&h=4e595224\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3161973</a>"},{"pid":"d8f788534ee55dbee109c1c8fa3c586a694c5d8f","tid":2012989,"uid":240976,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"有疫苗但係唔夠樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e251366bf5ec17361fff2f7b9c2030ee3ff52b5","tid":2012989,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"笑撚左"},{"pid":"ab09678543a4bb0106583072f1f7714a62f390bf","tid":2012989,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"轉用住condom 裝咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a30f82c565b22ad14d8c83eeba8906d855eac","tid":2012989,"uid":9974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母唔夠玻璃樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e24041cad018bb31f882bde8603c6493f7087b","tid":2012989,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"有冇藥樽概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636628107c5b1db13b3c1c504d4da8489b3b8249","tid":2012989,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f4e24041cad018bb31f882bde8603c6493f7087b","tid":2012989,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"有冇藥樽概念股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"我都想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35bfbcbb93210ec4877068a71e596f0a10aa5f4","tid":2012989,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:42:12.000Z","msg":"人類滅亡原因：冇玻璃樽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec9477976af190cf377ad5de6ce96a6c83b1496","tid":2012989,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4e2404